        %h4.modal-title Via NJ Transit
      .modal-body
        %p The Fiesta is located very close to the Woodridge train station. It is accessible via the Pascack Valley line on NJ Transit.
        .directions
          %a{href: '#'}
            %h4 From Manhattan
          %ul
            %li Go to Penn Station. 5:11 is the latest train to get you to Woodridge before 6PM.
            %li Take any train that is listed SEC (Secaucus).
            %li Get off at Secaucus.
            %li Take the Pascack Valley line (Purple line) to Woodridge.
            %li Call a local cab and ask to be picked up.
          %a{href: '#'}
            %h4 From North Jersey heading south
          %ul
            %li Go to a train on the Pascack Valley line (Hackensack, Riveredge, Oradell, Montvale, Westwood, Hillsdale).
            %li Get off at Woodridge.
            %li Call a local cab and ask to be picked up.
      .modal-footer
        %button.btn.btn-primary{"data-dismiss" => "modal", type: "button"} OK

